	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Personally I went to Oasis at lvl 12, and stayed there until lvl 20. Not for the loot though, because its next to nothing, but great steady XP, and not too dangerous since the caymans and crocs are not agressive. Start with caymans, then crocs, then deepwater caymans and finally the tough deepwater crocs. Sand Giants and spectres are the only real threath, in addition to the named croc Lockjaw who spawns from time to time. I only died once here from lvl 12 to 20. I hunted close to the zone, at the beach by the specterlake, there is an inn close by, and i can recommend this place xp wise. Later you can go to SK and hunt birds, better loot, or the gnoll spires, also in SK, with great xp and loot. Safe hunting. Pulk Steelswinger in Cazic Thule<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
